{"tid":213260,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"速食文化到底係嚴重咗定只係浮咗上面","createTime":"2017-04-23T04:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T13:48:21.000Z","uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e02ee34591cc4b69b311dc8c2da3321095e6a096","tid":213260,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"PTGF Popcorn movie&nbsp;新假期 仲有好多好多嘅速食文化<br />\n其實每個年代都係哩啲人做主流<br />\n但係我哋哩一個年代算唔算癲峰<br />\n有內涵嘅人會俾人笑戇鳩<br />\n好似一定要去行捷徑 連去&quot;慢活&quot;都要速食"},{"pid":"2590e96961160ed53966ffe25eaf5eb4f264bf17","tid":213260,"uid":12536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪科技太發達 定係關從眾事"},{"pid":"3450dcaa6aa3d419ccde9e8130822df2832c990b","tid":213260,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪科技太發達 定係關從眾事</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係科技發達&gt;社交模式改變(簡單化)&gt;行為改變內在，內在都簡單化<br />\n千言萬語變咗一個like，正負皮"},{"pid":"4a35ed1386c3fca295b2a86cb4fcdae4dbf0e52d","tid":213260,"uid":106477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"社會/生活模式之下壓力大<br />\n<br />\n普通人日日返工有幾多時間可以深入專注一件事？<br />\n放假睇場戲都費時咁夜第日又返工<br />\n<br />\n可以有幾慢活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dbd73d4b32ceaf8ce895f58c06f1d382c634b9","tid":213260,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社會/生活模式之下壓力大<br />\n<br />\n普通人日日返工有幾多時間可以深入專注一件事？<br />\n放假睇場戲都費時咁夜第日又返工<br />\n<br />\n可以有幾慢活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速食會唔會更方便noble class支配草根階層<br />\n我都知好陰謀論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60bc3b26ac402e7c3980037117ca28b1ec0f79c","tid":213260,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"